ations and that, as anticipated by Friedman and Sorkin, for appropriate\nspatial topology, this sector contains states which display fermionic behaviour\nunder $2\\pi$ rotations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Dec 2014 19:26:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
