ry, into the\nsingle problem of classifying inequivalent sets of matrix product operator\nsymmetries that are defined purely in terms of a PEPS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Dec 2014 21:00:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2016 18:57:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2016 18:24:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-01"}
