}$ beyond the leading\nNewtonian approximation, which is comparable to the PN order derived in our\nprevious work for the energy flux to infinity at 22PN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Dec 2014 00:30:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Mar 2015 07:42:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-27"}
